'''Jean-François Fortin''' (born 12 January 1947 in [[Coulonges-sur-l'Autize]]) is a [[France|French]] businessman who was the chairman of [[Stade Malherbe Caen|SM Caen]], a [[Association football|football club]] in the French [[Ligue 1]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.biladi.fr/031171577-caen-el-arabi-dispose-dun-bon-de-sortie|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110401024534/http://www.biladi.fr/031171577-caen-el-arabi-dispose-dun-bon-de-sortie|archivedate=2011-04-01|title=Caen : El-Arabi dispose d'un bon de sortie|date=29 March 2011|work=France Biladi|language=French|accessdate=14 April 2011}}</ref> He was made a Chevalier of the [[Légion d'honneur]] in 2002.

